title: Still Picking the Best GTA Game Ever
description: We've narrowed it down to the final four, and now special guest Evan Narcisse (@EvNarc) has joined the club to decide the best GTA game of all time, between Vice City, San Andreas, GTA 4, and GTA 5. Four may enter but only one will leave.
author: thebestiesbizemail@gmail.com (The Besties)
